    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201070/extras/dfdd1e6783ee84b44cdfe19128abe61a.poster.avif?t=1772392721\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201070/extras/dfdd1e6783ee84b44cdfe19128abe61a.webm?t=1772392721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201070/extras/dfdd1e6783ee84b44cdfe19128abe61a.mp4?t=1772392721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《钢铁巨像 机甲觉醒》</strong>是一款 Rogue-lite 机甲动作射击游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典的俯视角射击模式，及随机强化与升级系统，使玩家可快速上手，尽情享受游戏带来的无限乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >眼花缭乱的爆炸，酣畅淋漓的打击感，以及让人身临其境的音效，将给玩家带来一场极致的视听盛宴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201070/extras/baa68c73f0925aad92b278a12ede10ec.poster.avif?t=1772392721\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201070/extras/baa68c73f0925aad92b278a12ede10ec.webm?t=1772392721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201070/extras/baa68c73f0925aad92b278a12ede10ec.mp4?t=1772392721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>巧妙运用红外对抗系统（IRCM）抵御源源不断的子弹和导弹攻击。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事线以近未来发现的远古武器为导火索展开，世界各国与企业之间各方势力由此卷入不可避免的激烈战争。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为主人公的玩家需要操纵名为<strong>“基加斯”</strong>的机甲，与前方数以万计的敌人激情对战，杀出一条血路生存下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201070/extras/7c589c5540709ff2b668948f083e45fd.poster.avif?t=1772392721\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201070/extras/7c589c5540709ff2b668948f083e45fd.webm?t=1772392721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201070/extras/7c589c5540709ff2b668948f083e45fd.mp4?t=1772392721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事背景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在国家与大型企业之间无休止的战争中，未来世界变得满目疮痍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在日益激烈的军备竞赛中，人类挖掘出沉睡已久的古代兵器“盖亚”，却发现它是人类的灾难本身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面临灭绝危机，国家与企业结成临时联盟，开始对抗盖亚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十年后，玩家作为次世代兵器“基加斯”的驾驶员候选实验体“阿尼玛”苏醒，在这个混乱时代迈出第一步。</p>",
